<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 20mm;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .header-table td {
            vertical-align: top;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .logo-cell {
            width: 80px;
        }
        .logo-cell img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .company-contact {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #0000EE;
        }
        .title-bar {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .booking-title {
            font-size: 24pt;
            color: #009600;
        }
        .booking-subtitle {
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        .form-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .form-table td {
            padding: 4px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .form-label {
            width: 22%;
        }
        .form-value {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 4px;
            min-height: 20px;
        }
        .form-value-wide {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 4px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #dcf0ff;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        .checkin-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .checkin-table td {
            padding: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .checkin-label {
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .checkin-value {
            background-color: #dcf0ff;
            font-size: 11pt;
            padding: 8px;
        }
        .payment-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .payment-table td {
            padding: 6px;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        .payment-value {
            background-color: #dcf0ff;
        }
        .ref-row {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-top: none;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 10pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .remarks {
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .remarks-title {
            font-size: 10pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .notes-box {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 8px;
        }
        .notes-title {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .notes-list {
            font-size: 9pt;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }
        .notes-list li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="logo-cell">
                <img src="classpath:/assets/logo.png" alt="Logo" />
            </td>
            <td>
                <div class="company-name">FRIENDLY WINGS TRAVEL COMPANY</div>
                <div class="company-contact">Email : friendlywings123@gmail.com</div>
                <div class="company-contact">Ph no : +91 8098597634</div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div class="title-bar">
    <div class="booking-title">Booking Confirmation</div>
    <div class="booking-subtitle">Please present either an electronic or paper copy of your hotel voucher upon check-in.</div>
</div>

<table class="form-table">
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Booking ID :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($bookingId)$bookingId#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Number of Rooms:</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($rooms)$rooms#{else}0#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Booking Reference No :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($bookingRef)$bookingRef#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Number of Extra Beds :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($extraBeds)$extraBeds#{else}0#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Client :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($client)$client#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Number of Adults :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($adults)$adults#{else}0#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Member ID :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($memberId)$memberId#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Number of Children :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($children)$children#{else}0#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Country of Residence :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($countryOfResidence)$countryOfResidence#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Room Type :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($roomType)$roomType#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Property :</td>
        <td class="form-value-wide" colspan="1">#if($property)$property#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Promotion :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($promotion)$promotion#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Hotel :</td>
        <td class="form-value-wide">#if($hotelName)$hotelName#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td class="form-label">Meals Included :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($mealsIncluded)$mealsIncluded#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Address :</td>
        <td class="form-value-wide">#if($address)$address#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td colspan="2" rowspan="2" style="font-size:9pt; vertical-align:middle;">
            For Full Promotion details and conditions see confirmation email
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Property Contact Number :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($propertyContactNumber)$propertyContactNumber#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="form-label">Hotel Contact Number :</td>
        <td class="form-value">#if($propertyContactNumber)$propertyContactNumber#{else}&nbsp;#end</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="info-box">
    <strong>Cancellation Policy:</strong> #if($cancellationPolicy)$cancellationPolicy#{else}This booking is Non-Refundable and cannot be amended or modified. Failure to arrive at your hotel or property will be treated as a No-Show and will incur a charge of 100% of the booking value (Hotel policy).#end
</div>

<div class="info-box">
    #if($benefitsIncluded)$benefitsIncluded#{else}Benefits Included Free WiFi#end
</div>

<table class="checkin-table">
    <tr>
        <td class="checkin-label">Check in:</td>
        <td class="checkin-value">
            #if($checkIn)$checkIn#{else}&nbsp;#end<br />
            #if($checkInTime)$checkInTime#{else}After 12:00 am#end
        </td>
        <td class="checkin-label">Check out:</td>
        <td class="checkin-value">
            #if($checkOut)$checkOut#{else}&nbsp;#end<br />
            #if($checkOutTime)$checkOutTime#{else}After 12:00 am#end
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:right;">
            <img src="classpath:/assets/signature.png" alt="Signature" style="width:80px; height:40px;" />
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<table class="payment-table">
    <tr>
        <td class="payment-value">Payment Method : #if($paymentMethod)$paymentMethod#{else}Visa#end</td>
        <td class="payment-value">Card No : #if($cardNo)$cardNo#{else}XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-1111#end</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="ref-row">
    Reference # for Guest: #if($guestRef)$guestRef#{else}#end
</div>

<div class="remarks">
    <div class="remarks-title">Remarks :</div>
    <div>#if($remarks)$remarks#{else}XXXXXX#end</div>
    <div>Guest List : #if($guestList)$guestList#{else}XXXXXX#end</div>
    <div><strong>All special requests are subject to availability upon arrival</strong></div>
</div>

<div class="notes-box">
    <div class="notes-title">Notes</div>
    <ul class="notes-list">
        <li><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> At check-in, you must present the credit card used to make this booking and a valid photo ID with the same name. Failure to do so may result in the hotel requesting additional payment or your reservation not being honored. If you have submitted additional documentation for a third party booking or paid via a different payment method, please disregard the note above.</li>
        <li>All rooms are guaranteed on the day of arrival. In the case of a no-show, your room(s) will be released and you will be subject to the terms and conditions of the Cancellation/No-Show Policy specified at the time you made the booking as well as noted in the Confirmation Email.</li>
        <li>In cases where Breakfast is included with the room rate, please note that certain hotels may charge extra for children travelling with their parents. If applicable, the hotel will bill you directly. Upon arrival, if you have any questions, please verify with the hotel.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
